 Core Responsibilities:
 AI Project Leadership  - Develop a robust data and AI strategy for the project area of ownership, defining and managing the project with leadership team and stakeholders
 Analytics & Project Execution  : Drive analytics/AI projects forward to generate insights and make optimal impact; design data science algorithm and conduct EDA, if possible; Distill and communicate complex data insights to business users and cross-functional leaders/teams
 Strategy  : Drive project vision and strategy, and create capabilities that data science teams can leverage when generating insights for appropriate collaborators at Vertex aimed to improve human health
 Innovation  : Identifying new data science opportunities based on research, industry trends and best practices, driving data-driven innovation for the biotech intended for patient level impact across diseases
 Business Assessment:  Understand business requirements and translate into data strategy; identify new projects
 Technical Development:  Develop required technical skills to lead an AI project through internal and external courses
 Collaboration  : Working with cross-functional team, and build strong relationships with key internal and external customers (data scientists, data engineers, GIS, Privacy, and other business teams) that will allow understanding gaps
 ROI Calculation  Define and measuring key performance indicators to evaluate and understand insight value, product ROI, etc
 Company Information
 Vertex is a global biotechnology company that invests in scientific innovation.
